data.description: This home is Beautifully located in a quiet Cul-de-sac and is close to shopping, Fort Carson, and has easy access to the highway. The kitchen has an open feel with bright lighting. Laminate wood flooring throughout the house. New roof shingles were installed on the home and "Tuff Shed"in 2018.  Newer carpet. Vivent Security system is included with the home, buyer will need to subscribe for serivce. Radon Mitigation system installed in 2018.
